product_name: MorpheDripglass Glazed High Shine Lip Gloss
summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsCruelty FreeGet glazed and glistening with Morphe's Dripglass Glazed High Shine Lip Gloss. This nourishing formula, infused with plant-derived squalane & vitamin E, glides on juicy, semi-sheer, buildable, non-sticky color. Available in two finishes, it glazes lips in glass-effect or naturally shimmering shine.
details: DetailsBenefitsSemi-sheer, buildable coverageGlass-effect or naturally shimmering finishesNourishing, non-sticky feelFormulated with plant-derived squalane & vitamin EKey IngredientsPlant-derived squalaneVitamin EResearch Results93% of users agreed it looked flawless alone or layered over lipstick*100% of users agreed it glides on easily and precisely*93% of users agreed lips look more voluminous**Based on a study of 30 female lip gloss and lipstick users.Item 2612025How To UseApply one coat for a sheer, high-shine wash of color. Apply a second coat to dial up the shine. To up the opacity, apply Morphe's Soulmatte Filling Gel Lip Liner and Soulmatte Velvet Lip Mousse (both sold separately) before Dripglass.IngredientsPink Mirror: Polyisobutene, Octyldodecanol, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Hydrogenated Styrene/Isoprene Copolymer, Bis-Diglyceryl Polyacyladipate-2, Synthetic Wax, Stearalkonium Hectorite, Mica, Phenoxyethanol, Propylene Carbonate, Fragrance (Parfum), Squalane, Tocopheryl Acetate, Aluminum Hydroxide, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-di-t-butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Tin Oxide, Benzyl Alcohol, Hydroxycitronellal, Benzyl Salicylate, Hexyl Cinnamal. May Contain/Peut Contenir (+/-): Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Red 7 (CI 15850), Red 6 Lake (CI 15850), Yellow 5 Lake (CI 19140).

faceoff_positive.comments:
Welcome to my comprehensive review of the Dripglass Drenched High Pigment Lip Gloss in the captivating shade of Mauve Splash. This lip gloss is a testament to the brand's commitment to excellence, offering a richly pigmented formula that floods your lips with color while providing a glossy finish. Join me as I explore the packaging, texture, color payoff, longevity, and overall performance of this remarkable product.

Packaging:
The Dripglass Drenched High Pigment Lip Gloss arrives in an exquisite packaging that reflects the brand's commitment to luxury. The gloss comes in an elegant, transparent tube, allowing you to see the stunning Mauve Splash shade within. The sleek design features a secure cap adorned with the brand logo, adding a touch of sophistication. The compact and portable size of the tube makes it convenient to carry in your purse or pocket for on-the-go touch-ups.

Texture:
Upon application, the Dripglass Drenched Lip Gloss imparts a smooth and creamy texture that glides effortlessly onto the lips. The formula strikes a perfect balance between a lightweight feel and a lush, hydrating effect. It envelops your lips with a velvety-soft touch, creating a comfortable and non-sticky sensation. The lip gloss is skillfully formulated to ensure even and precise application, avoiding any clumping or unevenness.

Color Payoff:
Mauve Splash is a remarkable shade in the Dripglass Drenched High Pigment Lip Gloss range. It is a captivating mauve color with hints of rosy undertones that complement a wide range of skin tones. The rich pigmentation of the gloss delivers a saturated burst of color that instantly transforms your lips. Mauve Splash adds depth and dimension, enhancing the natural beauty of your pout. Whether worn alone for a statement lip or layered over your favorite lipstick, this shade exudes elegance and versatility.

Longevity:
The longevity of the Dripglass Drenched High Pigment Lip Gloss is truly impressive. Once applied, the gloss adheres to the lips, ensuring long-lasting wear without sacrificing its vibrancy. Even through sips and light snacking, the color remains intact, allowing you to enjoy a bold, beautiful lip look throughout the day. The gloss retains its lustrous shine and pigmentation, making it an ideal choice for extended wear or special occasions.

Performance:
The Dripglass Drenched High Pigment Lip Gloss truly excels in its performance. The formula not only provides intense color but also nourishes and conditions your lips. It is infused with nourishing oils and antioxidants that help moisturize and protect your lips from dryness and environmental factors. The gloss leaves your lips feeling supple, soft, and well-cared-for, ensuring a comfortable wear experience.

The glossy finish of the lip gloss adds a touch of allure and dimension to your lips, creating a visually plump and luscious effect. The high pigment content ensures that the color payoff is true to the tube, allowing you to achieve the desired intensity with just one swipe.

Conclusion:
In conclusion, the Dripglass Drenched High Pigment Lip Gloss in the shade Mauve Splash is a must-have for any lip gloss enthusiast. From its luxurious packaging to its smooth texture, rich color payoff, long-lasting formula, and nourishing benefits, this lip gloss is a standout product. Enhance your lip game with Mauve Splash and indulge in its velvety-soft texture and captivating color. Let your lips make a bold statement with this drenched and pigmented lip gloss from Dripglass.
faceoff_positive.headline: Would purchase in the future!

faceoff_negative.comments: I received this product for free in exchange for my honest review. The product's packaging is clear and it weighs nicely. From the outside, I was worried that this shade would be too light for my lips. However, upon applying this product to my lips, I see that it goes on smoothly and blends in very well. It does not leave white stuff around your lips either. What throws me off about this product is that although it looked good on my skin tone, it did not look that appetizing on my mother, who is a few shades darker. I have attached a video of what it looks like on my skin, and you can see that it has an orangey undertone, which does not go well with my mother's shade. Since the gloss is nude, I expected it to blend well, but it unfortunately did not.
faceoff_negative.headline: An Okay Product
